thread.title: BRIEF-India's Wipro March-Qtr Consol Profit Falls About 20 Pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-India's Wipro March-Qtr Consol Profit Falls About 20 Pct

organizations.name: wipro march-qtr consol profit falls about

text:
April 25 (Reuters) - Wipro Ltd:
* MARCH QUARTER CONSOL NET PROFIT 18.03 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS PROFIT OF 22.61 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* CONSENSUS FORECAST FOR MARCH QUARTER CONSOL PROFIT WAS 21.32 BILLION RUPEES
* MARCH QUARTER CONSOL REVENUE FROM OPERATIONS 137.69 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 139.88 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* MARCH QUARTER CONSOL IT SERVICES SEGMENT REVENUE 134.12 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 134.02 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR Source text - bit.ly/2HL5FrB Further company coverage:
